Bootstrap: docker
From: rockylinux:9
Stage: build

%files
mpi_hello_world.c /usr/local/src/mpi_hello_world.c

%post
dnf -y install openmpi-devel
/usr/lib64/openmpi/bin/mpicc -o /usr/local/bin/mpi_hello_world /usr/local/src/mpi_hello_world.c

Bootstrap: docker
From: rockylinux:9
Stage: final

%files from build
/usr/local/bin/mpi_hello_world

%post
chmod +x /usr/local/bin/mpi_hello_world
dnf install -y openmpi
dnf clean all

%labels
app mpi_hello_world
mpi openmpi
